Problem:
@EmmanuelMacron Ukraine is grateful to the French people for shelter. But the policy of appeasing the aggressor will sooner or later lead to a well-known result. If Ukraine does not stand up, millions of refugees will pour into Europe and no low gas prices from Russia will help.

@EmmanuelMacron Mariupol city council reports deaths of hunger in the city. Says many are starving. This is happening in Europe now. The Russians surrounded the city. Do not miss the humanitarian convoy. Refugees are not released. Don’t tell me that the world can’t do more to prevent this.

Solution:
@EmmanuelMacron #ArmUkraineNow Give weapons for Ukraine and you won't need to give money for refugees. Ukrainians have their home. We need heavy weapons right now. It is the matter of our lives and freedom. 

Remedy:
@EmmanuelMacron Children in Mariupol live in bombshells for over 50 days. In a completely blocked and for 90% destroyed City. Only internationally united guarantees from the world community and leaders can help those children to survive. Don’t let them die, like 205 others and thousands injured.

@EmmanuelMacron Give weapons for Ukraine and you won't need to give money for refugees. Ukrainians have their home. We need heavy weapons right now. It is the matter not only of our lives and freedom. Ukraine is fighting for the whole Europe now! #ArmUkraineNow

